{"tid":1394163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎智英助手: 「特朗普」與「香港示威」可能係俾華爾街日報抹黑","createTime":"2019-08-01T10:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T06:14:10.000Z","uid":134071,"like":264,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa0456659be7128f9ffbaf7a3f43f1794024583","tid":1394163,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:21:05.000Z","msg":"華爾街日報今日報導: Donald Trump要求美國官員對「香港示威」的發言要保持克制<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8A%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%A6%81%E5%AE%BD%E5%AE%B9-11564628408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25AE%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2591%2598%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2597%25AE%25E9%25A2%2598%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25AF%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%25AE%25BD%25E5%25AE%25B9-11564628408&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=4a908043\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%8A%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E8%A6%81%E5%AE%BD%E5%AE%B9-11564628408</a></span><br />\n<br />\n黎智英親蜜助手Mark Simon一向超級支持Donald Trump.<br />\n<br />\nMark Simon話華爾街日報既報導可能係fake news.  最大問題: 華爾街日報那篇報導唔只又幫中共洗白, 又將現在既「香港示威」老屈成「港獨革命」. &nbsp;<br />\n但Mark Simon認為唔可以忽略呢D疑似fake news, 因為呢D疑似fake news會累死香港.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1156766055991087104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1156766055991087104&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=39e5ca78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F11567660559910